interwikiextracts-error: Generic error message when an error occurred while getting the content
interwikiextracts-no-api: Error message when the specified wiki has no API defined
interwikiextracts-missing-title: Error message when the specified page was not found
interwikiextracts-no-such-section: Error message when the specified section was not found
interwikiextracts-invalid-section: Error message when the specified section is invalid, it must be an integer
